scenarios.name: Aggressive Action
scenarios.desc: Maximum civic investment, full AI charter enforcement, and 25% climate capex. Dividends at 10% redistribute gains broadly. Every structural lever pulled.

scenarios.name: Moderate Reform
scenarios.desc: Meaningful but cautious reform. 5% civic dividends, AI charter adopted, 25% climate spending. Progress without full structural overhaul.

scenarios.name: Business as Usual
scenarios.desc: Current trajectory continues. Minimal 2% dividends, no AI charter, modest 15% climate investment. Existing policies roll forward without structural change.

scenarios.name: Worst Case
scenarios.desc: Lowest intervention across every lever. 2% dividends, no AI governance charter, 15% climate capex. Institutions weaken as challenges compound.
